title: Grateful Dead Live at Hershey Park Stadium on 1985-06-28

Comment
Rained throughout show
Jerry wore a blazer over his usual T-shirt

Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
